          "You've always chaffed at the idea that the Ventrue have all the money and wealth and Brujah are just thugs. You may be an ex-athlete, but you aren't a thug, and can manage as well or better than most of them. LA might be a great place to prove yourself - if you can get around the Anarchs who are determined to keep showing their ass left and right."
